    </div>
    <%if false %>
     <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
      <img class="img-rentengle" src="images/LTTF2016shirts140x140.jpg">
      <h2><font color='blue'>桌盟球衣訂購</font></h2>
      <p>桌盟專屬球衣訂購專頁(550元/件）</p>
      <p><a> <%= link_to "前往訂購",shopcarts_path,:class=> "button radius"%></a></p>
    </div>
    <%end%>
    <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
      <img class="img-circle" src="images/ttcourts.jpg">
      <h2><font color='blue'>台灣打桌球地圖</font></h2>
      <p>全台灣各地桌球場地相關資料</p>
      <p><a> <%= link_to "查看地圖",ttcourts_path,:class=> "button radius"%></a></p>
